TITLE: Nesting Kernel in Silverstripe CMS (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This example illustrates how to nest the Kernel to modify global application state temporarily. It creates a new Kernel instance nested from the old one, modifies configuration, and then activates the old Kernel to revert the changes.
