TITLE: Custom Type Formatter Implementation
DESCRIPTION: PHP implementation of a custom type formatter for GraphQL types.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silverstripe/developer-docs/blob/5/en/02_Developer_Guides/19_GraphQL/02_working_with_dataobjects/01_adding_dataobjects_to_the_schema.md#2025-04-21_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: php
CODE:
```
namespace App\GraphQL;

class Formatter
{
    public static function formatType(string $className): string
    {
        $parts = explode('\\', $className);
        if (count($parts) === 1) {
            return $className;
        }
        $first = reset($parts);
        $last = end($parts);

        return $first . $last;
    }
}
```

