TITLE: Implementing Many-Many Relationships with Extra Fields
DESCRIPTION: Complete example showing how to implement many-many relationships with extra fields in DataObjects and GridField configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silverstripe/developer-docs/blob/5/en/02_Developer_Guides/03_Forms/Field_types/04_GridField.md#2025-04-21_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: php
