TITLE: Performing SQL INSERT in SilverStripe ORM
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use SQLInsert to perform an INSERT operation on the SiteTree table. It demonstrates adding multiple rows, adjusting assignments, and retrieving column names.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silverstripe/developer-docs/blob/5/en/02_Developer_Guides/00_Model/08_SQL_Select.md#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: php
