TITLE: Transforming Redux Action Types
DESCRIPTION: Example of transforming one action type to another before passing to the original reducer.
SOURCE: https://github.com/silverstripe/developer-docs/blob/5/en/02_Developer_Guides/15_Customising_the_Admin_Interface/08_ReactJS_Redux_and_GraphQL.md#2025-04-21_snippet_30

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export default (originalReducer) => (getGlobalState) => (state, { type, payload }) => {
  switch (type) {
    case 'REMOVE_ERROR': {
      // we'd like to archive errors instead of removing them
      return originalReducer(state, {
        type: 'ARCHIVE_ERROR',
        payload,
      });
    }
    default: {
      return state;
    }
  }
};
```

