TITLE: Entwine Namespaces and Scope
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how functions within an Entwine namespace can call other functions, either within the same namespace or in the base namespace. The `bar` function within the 'foo' namespace calls `baz` within the same namespace and `qux` in the base namespace.
