SOURCE: https://github.com/silverstripe/developer-docs/blob/5/en/02_Developer_Guides/15_Customising_the_Admin_Interface/07_jQuery_Entwine.md#2025-04-21_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
```js
$.entwine('foo', ($) => {
  $('div').entwine({
    bar() {
      this.entwine('.').baz();
    },
  });
});
```
